(3, '2013-10-29', 'La miroiterie \r\n88 rue de MÃ©nilmontant\r\n75020 Paris France', 'Paris - Clipping & Terrificolor', '<p><strong>Terrificolor</strong> est invit&eacute; par MMC pour soutenir la venue &agrave; Paris de<span class=\"fsl\"><strong> Clipping</strong> (SubPop, Deathbomb Arch), g&eacute;nial trio noise rap californien avec Jonathan Snipes (ex-Captain Ahab)!</span></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://clppng.bandcamp.com/album/midcity\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"fsl\">http://clppng.bandcamp.com/album/midcity</span></a></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\"><strong>Terrificolor</strong> (TTT, The Centrifuge) et son breakcore au germanium fait de larsen et bricodage.</span></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://terrificolor.bandcamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"fsl\">http://terrificolor.bandcamp.com/</span></a></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\">Plus un DJ set de cassettes rares d\'indus ou de rythmicnoise 80s par <strong>Sinead O\' Connick Jr.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/sinead-oconnick-jr\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/sinead-oconnick-jr</a></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\">&agrave; la Miroiterie (88 rue de Menilmontant : M&eacute;tro M&eacute;nilmontant)<br /> 20h-23h // 5 euros</span></p>\r\n<p>fb :</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/214746515315606/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/214746515315606/</a></p>', '29_10_2013_paris_clipping_terrificolor.jpg', 1),
(4, '2013-10-31', 'Le Buffet Froid\r\n91 MontÃ©e de la Grande-CÃ´te 69001 Lyon', 'Lyon - riddim collision w: C_C', '<p>JEUDI 31 OCTOBRE 2013 : <strong>Soir&eacute;e Barbars dans le cadre du festival riddim collision @ Lyon 1er</strong><br /> <br /> LE PRINCIPE : UN SEUL ET UNIQUE PASS ACHET&Eacute; 6&euro; DONNE ACC&Egrave;S AUX 5 BARS.</p>\r\n<p>Les Valseuses (1 Rue Chappet, Lyon 1er) :<br /> NON 5ILENT + VINCENT BLACK + PAD<br /> <br /> Le Kraspek Myzik (20 Mont&eacute;e Saint S&eacute;bastien, Lyon 1er) :<br /> GENERALE HYDROPHONICK + CRISTEL DUTORCHON + TOO GIRLY DJS<br /> <br /> Le Trokson (110 Mont&eacute;e de la Grande C&ocirc;te, Lyon 1er) : JESSICA 93 + SPLINT ! + D&Eacute;CHETS D&rsquo;OEUVRE<br /> <br /> Le Buffet Froid (91 mont&eacute;e de la grande c&ocirc;te, Lyon 1er) :<br /> MICHEL ANO&Iuml;A + C_C + INFECT &amp; BRK<br /> <br /> Les Capucins (5 Place des Capucins, Lyon 1er) :<br /> DAS SIMPLE + AMER/COLOR + MARILYN RAMBO</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Plus d\'info :</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.jarringeffects.net/fr/news/195_riddim-collision-festival-15-lyon-du-10-oct-au-10-nov-2013\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jarringeffects.net/fr/news/195_riddim-collision-festival-15-lyon-du-10-oct-au-10-nov-2013</a></p>', '31_10_2013_lyon_riddim_collision_w_C_C.jpg', 0),
(5, '2013-11-03', 'Urban Spree\r\nRevaler Str. 99 10245 Berlin', 'Berlin - Contort 7 w: C_C', '<p><strong>Contort #7 at Urban Spree</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>+++Main Room+++</strong><br /> Covered In Sand (Mira)<br /> Violet Poison (live) (Hospital Productions)<br /> Samuel Kerridge (dj) (Downwards)<br /> Dalglish (PAN)<br /> Lumisokea (Opal Tapes)<br /> Lop Lop (Dead Fader and C_C) (live)<br /> The Ambassador of Trouts (live)<br /> <strong>+++Bunker+++</strong><br /> Plaegium (live) 6 hour set</p>\r\n<p><strong>Visuals</strong> / Jolene Borrelli<br /> <strong>Art</strong> / Anastasia Andrieu and Elisabeth Hannah Neid</p>\r\n<p>Date / Sunday, 3 November 2013<br /> Time / 12:00 (noon) - 21:00<br /> Venue / Urban Spree / Revaler Str. 99, 10245 Berlin, Germany<br /> Cost / 2e</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.residentadvisor.net/event.aspx?520567\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.residentadvisor.net/event.aspx?520567</a></p>\r\n<p>Contort is a Sunday daytime event that focuses on the more Experimental Side of Electronic music.<br /> This is NOT just \"another\" techno/house party.</p>\r\n<p>Our concept is to take artists out of their usual environment and give them the freedom to experiment with music.<br /> Contort is a place you can chill, have a dance, do whatever you like, surrounded by like minded people, listening to artists playing something out of the ordinary in an extraordinary surrounding.</p>', '03_11_2013_berlin_contort_7_w_C_C.jpg', 0),
(6, '2013-11-06', 'Lauschangriff\r\nRigaer Str 103\r\n10247 Berlin', 'Berlin - Noiseangriff 38 w: C_C', '<p>PURE</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://pure.test.at\" target=\"_blank\">http://pure.test.at</a></p>\r\n<p>MARY ON LOW BLEACH</p>\r\n<p>COMPANY FUCK<br /> <a href=\"http://www.companyfuck.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.companyfuck.com/</a></p>\r\n<p>C_C<br /> <a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/c_c\" target=\"_blank\">http://soundcloud.com/c_c</a></p>\r\n<p>fgnugn</p>\r\n<p>ZFE</p>\r\n<p>CHRISTOPH FRINGELI</p>\r\n<p>starting 9pm!!!<br /> NoiseAngriff is a night taking place every first and third wednesday of the month.<br /> It is meant to be an &ldquo;early&rdquo; night (by Berlin standards), meaning that we will go till one or two and then it will depend on the audience, the bar staff as well as ourselves if we carry on and make it a late one after all.<br /> Entrance fee is just a free donation.</p>\r\n<p>Incl. Praxis Record stall!<br /> check <a href=\"http://praxis.c8.com/shop\" target=\"_blank\">http://praxis.c8.com/shop</a> and pick up your order at the party where you can also browse through and listen to a selection of our stock!</p>\r\n<p>NEW Datacide 13 and NEW Praxis 51 12&Prime; by Noize Creator will be available on the evening!</p>\r\n<p>You can find records, clothes and posters by Praxis (&nbsp;<a href=\"http://praxis.c8.com/shop\" target=\"_blank\">http://praxis.c8.com/shop</a> ) , Berzerk (&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.berzerk-produkts.net/v2/shop\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.berzerk-produkts.net/v2/shop</a> ) , YaYa23/Cyberrise and Digital Junk also from Thursday to Saturday, 3pm-8pm in YAYA23 Record Shop, Lenbachstr.9, 10245 Berlin Ostkreuz.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://noiseangriff.wordpress.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://noiseangriff.wordpress.com/</a><br /> <a href=\"http://www.mixcloud.com/NOISEANGRIFF/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mixcloud.com/NOISEANGRIFF/</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Lauschangriff.Berlin\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Lauschangriff.Berlin</a></p>', '06_11_2013_berlin_noiseangriff_38.jpg', 0),
(7, '2013-11-07', 'CafÃ© Central\r\n14 rue borgwal 1000 Brussels', 'Bruxelles - Antagon Ist & Exoterrism', '<p><strong>Antagon Ist</strong> ( Bruits de Fond / Nohmad) - Live / Mix<br /> <strong>Exoterrism</strong> ( ThirdType Tapes ) - Live<br /> <strong>Sub Altern</strong> ( Fast ) - Live<br /> <strong>Dubanity</strong> ( Fast ) - Dj<br /> <strong>Viktor Frensh</strong> ( Fast ) - Dj<br /> <strong>Bob&eacute; Van J&eacute;zu</strong> ( Fast ) - Dj</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Dark Dub (Step) / Hip Hop / Bass / Experiments</span></p>\r\n<p>07/11/2013, 21h</p>\r\n<p><br /> Caf&eacute; Central<br /> 14 rue borgwal, 1000 Brussels</p>', '07_11_2013_bruxelles_antagon_ist_exo.jpg', 0),
(8, '2013-11-16', 'Les Instants ChavirÃ©s\r\n7 rue Richard Lenoir Montreuil\r\n', 'Paris - Chanson Francaise w: N\'alov', '<p><strong>Chanson Fran&ccedil;aise D&eacute;g&eacute;n&eacute;r&eacute;e # 6</strong></p>\r\n<p>une soir&eacute;e en hommage &agrave; Fauve, le nouveau groupe de chanson fran&ccedil;aise engag&eacute;e. Avec que des reprises de Fauve, par :</p>\r\n<p><strong> SIDA</strong><br /> \"Quatre jeunes gens dans le vent, originaires des quartiers bourgeois de Lyon et Strasbourg. Ils ont abandonn&eacute; leurs &eacute;tudes en BTS force de vente pour prendre des drogues et faire du bruit.\"<br /> \"R&eacute;sultat : de jolies cassettes sur des labels Star Acad&eacute;mie (Tanzprocesz, Rank Toy) et des relations adult&eacute;rines avec la Grande Triple Alliance Internationale de l\'Est (Feeling of Love, The Dreams...)\"<br /> \"Pour r&eacute;pondre &agrave; une question souvent pos&eacute;e : oui, tous les membres du groupe ont le sida.\"<br /> \"La presse dit : \"un croisement entre no wave et noise rehauss&eacute; d\'un synth&eacute; cheap\", \"un bordel punk aussi dynamique que jouissif\", \"guitare incertaine, batterie enfum&eacute;e, chant hyst&eacute;rique\". Ok.\"</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://maisonderetraite.bandcamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://maisonderetraite.bandcamp.com/</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://sweetrotrecords.bandcamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://sweetrotrecords.bandcamp.com/</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>FOLK &Agrave; CHIER</strong><br /> \"Ils sont deux, ils ont des guitares, ils se d&eacute;foulent comme des gamins trisomiques. C\'est du folk parce que c\'est de la guitare acoustique, et \"&agrave; chier\" parce que la plupart des gens trouvent &ccedil;a &agrave; chier. Donc &ccedil;a s\'appelle Folk &agrave; chier. Voil&agrave;.\"<br /> \"&Agrave; votre gauche : Roro Perrot, alias Vomir. Figure abrasive de la harsh noise, ma&ccedil;on pour murs monolithiques de bruit statique, collaborateur de RedSK, Marc Hurtado, et bien d\'autres. &Agrave; votre droite : Yves Botz, alias Yves Botz. Guitariste poss&eacute;d&eacute;, &eacute;duc-sp&eacute; pour autistes japonais (Junko, Masayoshi Urabe), chaman du bruit avec les Dust Breeders ou Mesa of the Lost Women.\"<br /> \"De la noise oldschool, du folk animal, de la country de banlieue. Instinct, urgence, humour, bruit. Les quatre mains de ces deux idiots magnifiques font tout &ccedil;a.\"</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://roroperrot.bandcamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://roroperrot.bandcamp.com/</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.decimationsociale.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.decimationsociale.com/</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>N\'ALOV</strong><br /> \"La bande-originale d\'un h&ocirc;pital psychiatrique. Des textes crach&eacute;s, un chaos sonore qui met mal &agrave; l\'aise, une performance en camisole de force.\"<br /> \"De la po&eacute;sie bruitiste, industrielle. Yogi Data : machines, breakcore, power-electro. Bernard Brute : mots, cris, invectives. Whitehouse rencontre Fran&ccedil;ois Villon. Freaky post-exotic trance.\"</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://nhalov.bandcamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://nhalov.bandcamp.com/</a></p>\r\n<p>7&euro; | 20 : 30 | Les Instants Chavir&eacute;s<br /> 7 rue Richard Lenoir, Montreuil<br /> m&eacute;tro Robespierre</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.instantschavires.com/spip.php?article909\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instantschavires.com/spip.php?article909</a></p>', '16_11_2013_paris_chanson_fr.jpg', 0),
(9, '2013-11-20', 'Square de la Montjoie\r\n93210 Saint-Denis', 'Paris - Festival Nemo w: Exoterrism+C_C', '<p><strong>City Lights Orchestra Festival N&eacute;mo w/ Exoterrism</strong></p>\r\n<p><br /> <span class=\"fsl\">Mercredi 20 novembre 19h-23h<br /> Square de la Montjoie, Saint-Denis<br /> RER B La Plaine<br /> M&eacute;tro ligne 12 Front populaire<br /> Bus 153 et 239 arr&ecirc;t la Montjoie<br /> <span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Bus 302 arr&ecirc;t Encyclop&eacute;die-M&eacute;tallurgie<br /> <br /> Cette ann&eacute;e, dans le cadre du festival N&eacute;mo (le rendez-vous arts num&eacute;riques d\'Arcadi Ile-de-France), Synesth&eacute;sie vous propose une exp&eacute;rience tout nouvelle avec l\'&oelig;uvre d\'Antoine Schmitt \"City Lights Orchestra\".<br /> <br /> Pr&eacute;sent&eacute;e pour la premi&egrave;re fois au Cap en Afrique du Sud, cette &oelig;uvre m&ecirc;lant organique, syst&egrave;me g&eacute;n&eacute;ratif et lumi&egrave;res puls&eacute;es sera propos&eacute;e aux habitants de la Plaine.<br /> Il suffira aux participants de se connecter via leur ordinateurs, tablettes et smartphones sur citylightsorchestra.net pour faire partie int&eacute;grante de l\'&oelig;uvre.<br /> <br /> Rejoigez-nous dans le square de la Montjoie, d&egrave;s la tomb&eacute;e de la nuit, le 20 novembre et profitez du spectacle lumineux.<br /> <br /> Autour de City Lights Orchestra de 19h &agrave; 23h seront organis&eacute;s divers &eacute;v&eacute;nements.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\"><span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/514668085283703\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/514668085283703</a></span></span></p>', '20_11_2013_paris_festival_nemo.jpg', 0),
(10, '2013-11-30', '', 'Geneve - Free Market 13 w: C_C', '<p>le Free Market revient pour la septi&egrave;me ann&eacute;e dans une ambiance Moto Vintage. Pour l&rsquo;occasion La Bulle pose ses top cases dans l&rsquo;ex Moto Shop situ&eacute; boulevard du Grand Cerf en face du Plan B. Dans un univers vintage et&nbsp;d&eacute;cal&eacute;&nbsp;venez d&eacute;couvrir des plasticiens, des stylistes ( v&ecirc;tements, chapeaux ), des cr&eacute;ateurs de bijoux, sacs &agrave; mains, du mobilier, de la s&eacute;rigraphie&hellip; Chaque soir&eacute;e sera cl&ocirc;tur&eacute;e par des concerts d&rsquo;artistes finement d&eacute;got&eacute;s. Enfin, une exposition BD sur &laquo;&nbsp;Jour de Poisson&nbsp;&raquo; d&rsquo;Amandine Ciosi, aux &eacute;ditions Scutella, vous sera propos&eacute;e tout au long de l&rsquo;&eacute;v&egrave;nement.</p>\r\n<p>La Bulle vous attends d&egrave;s 16 heures le vendredi 29 novembre. Les concerts auront lieu &agrave; 22h au Plan B, avec au programme Sathonay, Rature et Komissar Koko. Les hostilit&eacute;s reprennent le samedi 30 &agrave; 14h avec des concerts &agrave; partir de 20h cette fois ci dans l&rsquo;ancien mocal moto, &agrave; savoir Trotsky Nautique, Samba de la Muerte, Les Morts Vont Bien et C_C. Enfin rejoignez nous le dimanche 1er d&eacute;cembre &agrave; partir de 14h, pour une maxi boum qui sera organis&eacute;e pour les enfants &agrave; partir de 16h, suivi &agrave; partir de 17h de deux artistes qui auront carte blanche pour rendre cet &eacute;v&egrave;nement inoubliable et cl&ocirc;tur&eacute; la session Moto Vintage Style !</p>\r\n<p>A noter que ceux qui porteront un casque sur la t&ecirc;te en entrant gagneront un badge &eacute;dition limit&eacute;e !!</p>\r\n<p>Liste des cr&eacute;ateurs et cr&eacute;atrices participant :</p>\r\n<p>Guig, Babalove, <a href=\"http://www.odettepicaud.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Odette Picaud</a>, Rachel La Prairie, <a href=\"http://orange.tp.over-blog.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Orange TP</a>, <a href=\"https://latelier86.wordpress.com/collection-automne-hiver-20112012/adele-toquoy/\" target=\"_blank\">ADL</a>, <a href=\"http://caferacer.livegalerie.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Cedric Ponge</a>, <a href=\"http://www.seb-russo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sebastien Russo</a>, Mamzelle Ad&egrave;le, <a href=\"http://nlemercier.jimdo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Natacha Lemercier</a>, <a href=\"http://www.alittlemarket.com/v/favorite_creator/list/milune-734323.html\" target=\"_blank\">Milune cr&eacute;ations</a>, <a href=\"http://www.alittlemarket.com/boutique/descoquelicotsdanslapoche-299419.html\" target=\"_blank\">Des Coquelicots dans la Poche</a>, <a href=\"http://www.laviedevantsoie.com/\" target=\"_blank\">La Vie Devant Soie</a>, Bijoux Hors du Temps, <a href=\"http://www.miriamvile.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Miriam Vile</a>, <a href=\"http://artefusion.canalblog.com/\" target=\"_blank\">ArtEfusion</a>, <a href=\"http://rosebouchon.canalblog.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rose Bouchon</a>, Mementomori, <a href=\"http://lamaisondeugenie.fr/\" target=\"_blank\">La Maison d&rsquo;Eug&eacute;nie</a>, Sandra Proux, <a href=\"http://lulupoisson.blogs.marieclaireidees.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Lulupoisson</a>, <a href=\"http://florent-rouaud.eklablog.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Les D&eacute;coupures de Fer</a>, Mr Machin, <a href=\"http://www.xorgin.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Xorgin</a>, <a href=\"http://www.alittlemarket.com/boutique/marie_bigoudie_et_jibe-406903.html\" target=\"_blank\">Jib&eacute; et Marie Bigoudie</a>, <a href=\"http://christellepennachio.blogspot.fr/\" target=\"_blank\">Chrtistelle Pennachio</a>, l&rsquo;Atelier Rose, <a href=\"http://www.isamayso-creation.com/index.php\" target=\"_blank\">Isa Mayso</a>, <a href=\"http://www.scutella.fr/\" target=\"_blank\">Scutella Editions</a>, <a href=\"http://www.guillainlevilain.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Guillain le Vilain</a>, Mathieu Furg&eacute;, Lieu de Mode</p>', '30_11_2013_geneve_free_market_13.jpg', 0),
(11, '2013-12-01', '4 rue de la prairie genÃ¨ve', 'Geneve - CONTAINER w: C_C', '<p><strong>CONTAINER w/ C_C</strong><br /> DIMANCHE 1er DECEMBRE &ndash; 21h00 (Concert 21h30&nbsp;!)<br class=\"autobr\" /> 4, RUE DE LA PRAIRIE<br /> &diams; punk stripped-down martellement low-fi irresistible beats evening &diams;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>CONTAINER</strong> (Usa)<br class=\"autobr\" /> Ren Schofield&nbsp;: electronics &amp; stripped-down beats</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://qujunktions.com/artists/container\" target=\"_blank\">http://qujunktions.com/artists/container</a><br class=\"autobr\" /> +<br class=\"autobr\" /> <strong>c_c</strong> (France)<br class=\"autobr\" /> Eduardo Ribuyo&nbsp;: electronics &amp; trance-down analogic beats</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/c_c\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/c_c</a><br class=\"autobr\" /> +<br class=\"autobr\" /> <strong>BAD TRIP INC.</strong> (ch)<br class=\"autobr\" /> passeurs de disques enrubannants</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.wildrfid.net/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wildrfid.net/</a></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;Fabuleux et sur-jouissif projet nous saluant depuis Providence aux States, CONTAINER (de son vrai nom Ren Schofield) sculpte des particules soniques punk et vicieuses en forme de marteaux-piqueurs rythmiques qui groovent de la mani&egrave;re la plus implacable, continue, irr&eacute;sistible et psych&eacute;d&eacute;lique qui soit, s&eacute;vissant actuellement dans le r&eacute;seau des musiques aventureuses.</p>\r\n<p>Les mailles low-fi de pattern de drum-machines maximis&eacute;es &agrave; fond, les boucles spiralantes et les arrangements hypnotiques de CONTAINER forment une musique live au poids et la fonction s&eacute;rieuse/cons&eacute;quente, capable de &agrave; la fois cr&eacute;er l&rsquo;&eacute;meute dans des clubs dancefloors aussi prestigieux que le Berghain berlinois et plonger les caves undergrounds de l&rsquo;Europe enti&egrave;re dans la soumission/abandon le plus total.</p>\r\n<p>D&eacute;but&eacute; en 2009 en r&eacute;ponse &agrave; sa d&eacute;couverte de la techno minimale des ann&eacute;es 90, CONTAINER combine des &eacute;l&eacute;ments de son background noise et de collages de cassettes avec un nouvel int&eacute;r&ecirc;t pour des beats r&eacute;p&eacute;titifs, cr&eacute;ant ce son rythmique d&eacute;rang&eacute; et jouissivement sauvage.</p>\r\n<p>Auteur de divers enregistrements cassette avant de sortir l&rsquo;excellent &laquo;&nbsp;LP&nbsp;&raquo; sur le label Spectrum Spools/Editions Mego, CONTAINER d&eacute;barque pour la premi&egrave;re fois &agrave; Gen&egrave;ve avec ces fabuleux rythmes abrasifs et &agrave; rendre fou et une pl&eacute;thore de nouveaux enregistrements sous le bras.</p>\r\n<p>Et en compl&eacute;ment de soir&eacute;e, d&rsquo;autres martellements beats analogiques d&eacute;vastateurs et ravag&eacute;s par l&rsquo;excellent &laquo;&nbsp;fouteur de feu&nbsp;&raquo; fran&ccedil;ais c_c, entraper&ccedil;u au d&eacute;tour de quelques soir&eacute;es par nos oreilles et corps accapar&eacute;s. Influenc&eacute; par le dub, la jungle, le breakcore, la musique industrielle et les musiques de transe en g&eacute;n&eacute;ral, c_c amalgame &agrave; grands coups d&rsquo;&eacute;chos et de larsens des rythmes et des sons d&rsquo;origines diverses. Son premier album&nbsp;: Retro/Action, est sorti en septembre 2012 sur Bedroom Research et Third Type Tapes. En live l&rsquo;exp&eacute;rience est enveloppante&nbsp;: les beats omnipr&eacute;sents et r&eacute;p&eacute;titifs, lents ou &eacute;pileptiques, sont taill&eacute;s &agrave; la hache et d&eacute;cupl&eacute;s par la saturation. De la basse-musique improvis&eacute;e qui crache, qui d&eacute;gouline et qui pulse&nbsp;!</p>\r\n<p>Le tout enrubann&eacute; par une s&eacute;lection de plaques vinyles de nos passeurs de disques pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute;s, les bad trip inc. (from wildrfid records).</p>\r\n<p>Bref, un excellent dimanche de punk-clubbing-trance-spirit &agrave; la cave12 ce soir.</p>\r\n<p>Dans le genre beat-visc&eacute;ral crissant, lourd, &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire et totalement d&eacute;nud&eacute;, franchement recommand&eacute;. Yeah&nbsp;!</p>\r\n<p>Plus d&rsquo;infos&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.cave12.org/CONTAINER-c_c-BAD-TRIP-INC\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cave12.org/CONTAINER-c_c-BAD-TRIP-INC</a></p>', '01_12_2013_geneve_CONTAINER_w_C_C.jpg', 0),
(12, '2013-12-07', 'FUGA\r\nNÃ¡mestie SNP 24 81101 Bratislava', 'Bratislava - MIKROZVUK w: Exoterrism', '<p><strong>MIKROedition of ZVUK</strong><span class=\"fsl\"> by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LOMlabel?directed_target_id=0\" target=\"_blank\">LOM Label</a><br /> #beyond #postmusic #freespirits<br /> <br /> Local stars + guests from Peru/Netherlands, Hong Kong/Brussels, Brno will meet at another LOM event in FUGA.<br /> <br /> ANDR&Aacute;S CS&Eacute;FALVAY<br /> <a href=\"https://zvukolom.org/releases/andras-csefalvay-funeral-the-musical/\" target=\"_blank\">http://zvukolom.org/releases/andras-csefalvay-funeral-the-musical/</a><br /> <br /> ANGAKOK &Theta;.<br /> <a href=\"http://poo.sk/\" target=\"_blank\">http://poo.sk/</a><br /> <br /> EXOTERRISM<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/exoterrism\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/exoterrism</a><br /> <br /> CHRIS GALARRETA<br /> <a href=\"https://aloblog.wordpress.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://aloblog.wordpress.com/</a><br /> <br /> LUCIE V&Iacute;TKOV&Aacute;<br /> <a href=\"https://zvukolom.org/releases/03-jolana-havelkova-lucie-vitkova-navrh-na-zmenu-partitury/\" target=\"_blank\">http://zvukolom.org/releases/03-jolana-havelkova-lucie-vitkova-navrh-na-zmenu-partitury/</a></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\">ODPAÅ<br /> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g8UV13vJgWk\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g8UV13vJgWk</a><br /> <br /> more infos : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/182122808656210\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/182122808656210</a></span></p>', '07_12_2013_bratislava_MIKROZVUK.jpg', 0),
(13, '2013-12-13', '', 'Luxembourg - Cessange w: Exoterrism', '<p><strong>Cessange Supercollider workshop</strong><br /> <br /> <span class=\"fsl\">In this workshop you will learn how to use and program your own analog and digital synthesizers and effects, using Supercollider.<br /> We will also learn how to use supercollider as a live instrument (livecoding) , how to interface it with external softwares hardwares, and finally we will create our own music, using patterns to switch on and off sounds to create rythms.<br /> This workshop is for all musicians interested in using supercollider or musicians who wish to understand common synthesis techniques. Advanced<span class=\"text_exposed_show\"> Supercollider users are also welcome to participate.<br /> <br /> Day 1<br /> <br /> Morning 10h-13h SuperCollider Basics<br /> ==========================<wbr />==========================<wbr />==================<br /> -SuperCollider Introduction to language and server,<br /> basic algorithms, Stochastic, Markov Chains,<br /> -Basic Sound Synthesis (Spectral Model , Abstract Model)<br /> <br /> Afternoon 14h-16h Advanced Sound Synthesis and Live Coding<br /> ==========================<wbr />==========================<wbr />==================<br /> -Pysical Model (Ruiz Strings, Karplus-Strong, Waveguide, ..)<br /> -Processed Recording (Granular Synthesis, Wavetable synthesis, Wavelet T,Sampling ...)<br /> -JitLib, Ndef, ProxySpace<br /> <br /> Day 2<br /> <br /> Morning 10h-13h Interactivity and Interfaces<br /> ==========================<wbr />==========================<wbr />==================<br /> -Interfacing with other hardwares softwares using Midi, OSC, Analog Synths, Midi Controllers,<br /> Gamepads.<br /> -Graphical User interface<br /> -Machine Listening , FFT<br /> <br /> Bring your controllers GamePads, Arduino, Wok, Frying Pan, Carrots, whatever...<br /> <br /> Day 2<br /> <br /> Afternoon 14h-16h Patterns Tasks Routines (Practical)<br /> ==========================<wbr />==========================<wbr />==================<br /> Create beats , Analog like Drum Machines , How to arrange your track etc..<br /> In this lesson we will learn Pdef, Tdef, Ndef, Routines, and Demand Rate.<br /> <br /> Day 3<br /> <br /> Afternoon 14h-16h Audiovisual with SC<br /> ==========================<wbr />==========================<wbr />==================<br /> Scoping, Mapping, Vectors, Animations</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\"><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">20 euros per day<br /> day 3 is 10 euros<br /> 30 euros for 3 days<br /> <br /> If the dates are a problem we can also for example rearrange the schedules<br /> for example:<br /> december 14th -15th<br /> 9-13h :: 14h-18h<br /> in two days the other schedule is a more laidback lazy schedule<br /> <br /> if everyone agrees but please pm before<br /> <br /> limited to 8 person maximum<br /> payment via paypal here before the 13th december 2013 :<br /> <a href=\"http://luxembourgsupercollider.blogspot.be/\" target=\"_blank\">http://<wbr />luxembourgsupercollider.blo<wbr />gspot.be/</a><br /> (at the bottom of the page)<br /> <br /> please specify in advance which day you would like to attend or if you would like to attend all 3 days<br /> you can also decide after the first day if you wish to continue the rest of the workshops the 3 days promotion will still be valid.<br /> <br /> Please install the latest Supercollider version before coming to the workshop (Mac, Win , Linux)<br /> install it for free here:<br /> <a href=\"http://supercollider.github.io/download.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://<wbr />supercollider.sourceforge.n<wbr />et/downloads/</a><br /> if you need help please pm or phone<br /> enquiries: +32466146950</span></span></p>', '13_12_2013_luxembourg_cessange.jpg', 0),
(14, '2013-12-14', '', 'Luxembourg - \"Ooh festival\"', '<p><strong>\"Ooh festival\" afterparty</strong><br /> <span class=\"fsl\">After the last concert (Robert Lippok) Exit has to get ready for the next day, so we plan to continue at Decibel! 3 artists will play:<br /> <br /> Rabhansl (Heidelberg) <a href=\"http://www.rabhansl.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rabhansl.com/</a><br /> <br /> Exoterrism (Hong Kong) <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/exoterrism\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/<wbr />exoterrism</a><br /> <br /> Mithraphreq (Berlin/Luxembourg) <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/mithraphreq\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/<wbr />mithraphreq</a><br /> <br /> Entrance is free if you attended the festival! otherwise it\'s 5 euro :)</span></p>', '14_12_2013_luxembourg_Ooh festival.jpg', 0),
(15, '2013-12-19', '', 'Karlsruhe - Angewandte Elektronik II', '<p><strong>Angewandte Elektronik II</strong><br /> <br /> <span class=\"fsl\">Bereits zum zweiten Mal l&auml;dt das AKK zu elektronischer Livemusik, fernab der<br /> Viva-Clubrotation. Wagt den Schritt in das AKK und erlebt die kompromissloseste<br /> Musikveranstaltung Karlsruhes seit Angewandte Elektronik 1. Zum<br /> Redaktionsschluss des Stadionheftes haben wir dabei schon die folgenden<br /> K&uuml;nstler gewinnen k&ouml;nnen:<br /> <br /> <span class=\"text_exposed_show\">Terrificolor (Breakcore)<br /> <br /> Auch dieses Mal wird Angewandte Elektronik eine internationale Veranstaltung, wenn Terrificolor aus Paris in die badische Hauptstadt reist. Im Gep&auml;ck hat er<br /> dabei reinsten dreckigen Breakcore. Hier wird gemixt, beschleunigt und gescratcht, dass jede Melodie und jeder Takt aus der Musik gewaltsam herausgepr&uuml;gelt wird, um dann aus den Ruinen des alten Musikgedankens einen<br /> eigenen Groove zu erschaffen. Electronic-doubletime dance-music, die s&auml;mtliche Nerven eures K&ouml;rpers unter Starkstrom setzt.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"http://terrificolor.bandcamp.com/album/n-50\" target=\"_blank\">http://terrificolor.bandcamp.com/album/n-50</a><br /> <br /> 0c (Glitch)<br /> <br /> Selbst dem K&uuml;nstlerkollektiv Hidden Paranoid Society zugeh&ouml;rig, erbaut der<br /> Karlsruher Klangwelten, die diesem Namen mehr als gerecht werden. Ohne<br /> treibende Musik wird der H&ouml;rer doch gleichsam zum Getriebenen der<br /> ungew&ouml;hnlichen Mixtur aus Ambient und Glitch. Die Spanne eines Auftritts reicht<br /> von der tanzbaren technischen St&ouml;rung &uuml;ber geisterhafte Szenen bis hin zum<br /> puren Noise. Kurz: eine elektronische Entdeckungsreise mit<br /> Horizonterweiterungsgarantie, die man unter keinen Umst&auml;nden verpassen sollte.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/coldcoldcold\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/coldcoldcold</a><br /> <br /> Noise is Silence is Noise (Electric Noise)<br /> <br /> Gerne live mit Kollaborationen unterwegs bewegte sich das Cham&auml;leon N(S)N neben<br /> Noise auch schon in ruhigeren Sph&auml;ren oder unterst&uuml;tzte analog produzierte<br /> Beats. Was nun solo aus der Wundert&uuml;te entspringt bleibt letzten Endes ein<br /> Geheimnis. Jedoch wurde ein &bdquo;h&auml;rteres Set&ldquo; bereits angek&uuml;ndigt. Auf verzerrte<br /> Audiosignale und Frequenzspiele darf sich also schon einmal gefreut werden,<br /> wenn die Maschinen erst einmal zum Leben erweckt werden. F&uuml;r das Auge ist<br /> dazukommend eine live gemixte Videoinstallation in Planung.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"http://noisebau.bandcamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://noisebau.bandcamp.com/</a><br /> <br /> AGIKAKALUNA! (Chiptunes)<br /> <br /> Aus begrenzten Mitteln mit anachronistischen Ger&auml;ten Musik machen. Im s&uuml;dlichen<br /> Teil Deutschlands d&uuml;rfte es darin keine bessere Person als AGIKAKALUNA! aus<br /> Erlangen geben. Mit seinen selbstmodifizierten Gameboys, die er f&uuml;r seine<br /> Auftritte verwendet, hat er es &uuml;ber die Jahre bereits zur Vorband von Casper<br /> und ins Fernsehen geschafft. F&uuml;r jeden, der auch nur entfernt mit chiptunes<br /> etwas anfangen kann, stellt der Besuch dieses Acts nicht weniger als eine<br /> Pflicht dar.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/agikakaluna\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/agikakaluna</a><br /> <br /> Nicht mehr im Stadionheft, trotzdem klasse:<br /> <br /> Gebild (Live-Techno)<br /> <br /> In tiefster Nacht kommt uns eine einzelne Drum Machine besuchen.<br /> Dahinter steht Gebild aus Karlsruhe, der nun schon bereits seit einigen<br /> Jahren minimalen und livehaftigen Techno aus dieser herauszaubert.<br /> Ohne jedwede Presets wird ein Auftritt somit zu einer unverf&auml;lschten<br /> Improvisation mit hypnotisch-tanzbarer Musik, welche eine Energie<br /> transportiert, nach der man in manchem Club lange suchen kann.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/gebild\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/gebild</a></span></span><br /> <br /> MORE INFOS : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/640661982634732\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/640661982634732</a></p>', '19_12_2013_karlsruhe_angewandte.jpg', 0),
(16, '2013-12-28', '', 'Den Haag - Villa 5 Jaar w: Exoterrism', '<p><strong>Villa 5 Jaar</strong><br /> <br /> <span class=\"fsl\">Celebrating the Villa\'s 5th birthday since the bold squat in 2008. For this occasion we have the pleasure of serving you with a line up of live performances &amp; DJ\'s that will lift up your party spirits to astronomic proportion..need to cool down? Outside we have Sauna and BBQ TOGO as well. Villa friends, party enthusiasts and free spirits, join in....<br /> <br /> </span><strong>Live Acts:</strong><span class=\"fsl\"><br /> - Carnival (Elektro Ocean Partee) (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/carnivalband\" target=\"_blank\">Carnival</a>)<br /> - ExoTerrism (Tech-Hop/SuperCollider) (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThirdTypeTapes\" target=\"_blank\">ThirdTypeTapes</a>)<br /> <br /> <span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><strong>DeeJay\'s:</strong><br /> - IrfieJ<br /> - Brother Louis<br /> - Jack Tulp &amp; Kenny Harder<br /> - Krank Pappa<br /> <br /> </span></span><strong>Carnival:</strong><span class=\"fsl\"><span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><br /> The Carnival project it&rsquo;s an Electronic Duo based in Den Haag(NL), created by Viola Zorzi (vocalist &amp; composer) and Marcello Mazzocco (keyboardist &amp; composer), active since December 2009.<br /> <br /> An eclectic and outside the lines show, a strong and motivating sound accompanied by a 360&deg; experience, made with colorful visuals, light games, olfactory elements and solid audio frequencies. Their influences allow them to always experiment with new rhythms and new sounds, surfing pleasantly on the electronic waves. Their performance faithfully accompanies their words, their message of Love. We would rather say a recommendation, an invitation to love and face life in perpetual contact with your inner child, keeping your brain creative, awaken, free and alight.<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/carnivalweb\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/carnivalweb</a><br /> <br /> <strong>Exoterrism:</strong><br /> Exoterrism is a chinese fugitif, ex-shaolin, triad of WanChai (Hong Kong). He\'s mainly manipulating Feng Shui, QiGong, Chaotic functions, and Algorithms to produce unstable phenomenons between dimensions. His influences are coming from radioactive frequencies, extra-sensorial perceptions, synaesthetics, post apocalyptic mayhem, the nasdaq stock market and the jungle.<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/exoterrism\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/exoterrism</a></span></span></p>', '28_12_2013_den_haag_villa_5_Jaar.jpg', 0),
(17, '2014-01-05', 'La miroiterie\r\n88 rue de MÃ©nilmontant\r\n75020 Paris France', 'Paris - TTT party', '<p><span class=\"fsl\">Marcel Du Swamp (US) = teenager en col&egrave;re<br /> <a href=\"http://swampswampswampswampswampswampswampswampswamp.bandcamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://swampswampswampswampswampswampswampswampswamp.bandcamp.com/</a><br /> <br /> <span class=\"text_exposed_show\">SFTSTPS (All) = collages / d&eacute;calages<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/sftstps\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/sftstps</a><br /> <br /> Toma Tello (Perou/Lux) = cumbia introspective<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/rivotriler\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/rivotriler</a><br /> <br /> Daniel Llermaly (Chili) = atari punk console<br /> <a href=\"http://www.oficinadesonido.org/\" target=\"_blank\">www.oficinadesonido.org</a><br /> <br /> City Dragon (Paris) = homme + saxo<br /> <a href=\"https://citydragon.bandcamp.com/album/dogs-dogs-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://citydragon.bandcamp.com/album/dogs-dogs-2</a><br /> <br /> Spoliature (Paris) = improvisions<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/c_c\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/c_c</a><br /> <br /> La miroiterie<br /> 88 rue de M&eacute;nilmontant<br /> XX&egrave;me<br /> <br /> PAF : 5 euros</span></span></p>\r\n<p>More infos : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1504510199773499\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1504510199773499</a></p>', '2014_01_05-miroiterie-paris.jpg', 0),
(18, '2014-01-07', 'The Student \r\n76 rue des Palais \r\n1030 Brussels', 'Bruxelles - TTT party', '<p><span class=\"fsl\">DJ set:<br /> <span class=\"text_exposed_show\">ê—ˆWeird Dust (Brussels, Be) tapes mix<br /> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tWwtN6L1u-E\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/<wbr />watch?v=tWwtN6L1u-E</a><br /> <br /> ê—ˆM&eacute;LODiK PiNPON (Brussels, Be)<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/melodikpinpon/m-lodik-pinpon-gothverdome-01\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/<wbr />melodikpinpon/<wbr />m-lodik-pinpon-gothverdome-<wbr />01</a><br /> <br /> <br /> Live:<br /> ê—ˆMARCEL DUSWAMP (Baltimore, USA)<br /> Ripped jeans, lumberjack shirt, crazy hairdo, foaming at the mouth, groove box on the dinner table, microphone in the hand, up for a good brawl. Marcel Du Swamp&rsquo;s artistic programme is typically a collage from the repertoire of classic teenage rebellion antics. The recombination of all-too-familiar material entails a potentiation of the supposedly simple. Put otherwise: One can only marvel at how bubbly the quagmire of adolescent emotional crap can explode in your face once again. Du Swamp makes punk with a beatbox: muffled bass, noise, screams &ndash; all sliders to the max. As is generally known, his famous foregoer Marcel Duchamp profiled himself in his later years as a chess champion. Thus all doors are open for Du Swamp&rsquo;s musical future. Chinese Chequers Core? Malefiz Metal? Trouble Techno?<br /> <a href=\"http://swampswampswampswampswampswampswampswampswamp.bandcamp.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://<wbr />swampswampswampswampswampsw<wbr />ampswampswampswamp.bandcam<wbr />p.com/</a><br /> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NoP9nskacqw\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/<wbr />watch?v=NoP9nskacqw</a><br /> <br /> <br /> ê—ˆSFTSTPS (Berlin, GER)<br /> SFTSTPS is the sound of computers with feelings. This means being human and using the wrong sound. This also means wonderment. This could also mean watching the world collap&shy;se. This is one or many people steeped in American top 40 through walls of egregious noise. This is seeing if you can bend the notes further and learning how to dance. This is ste&shy;aling sounds and seeing where they fall.<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/sftstps\" target=\"_blank\">http://soundcloud.com/<wbr />sftstps</a></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\"><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">ê—ˆ\"FYOELK (Antwerp, BE) Fyoelk reveals the solo adventures by two legs of freeform acid beat duo Laser Poodle, residing in Antwerp. After going through a period of improvised analog electronics, his newer sound explorations have returned to the track format, utilizing MIDI technology. Driven by a newfound love for primal Chicago house and cosmic disco, polymorphous synth sequences and tribal percussion blend into sonic wormholes. Fyoelk runs the cassette label Stenze Quo. <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fyoelk\" target=\"_blank\">http://soundcloud.com/<wbr />fyoelk</a> <a href=\"http://stenzequo.blogspot.be/\" target=\"_blank\">http://<wbr />stenzequo.blogspot.be/</a><br /> <br /> <br /> ê—ˆMERDRE ! (Brussels, Be) NOHMAD frequencies<br /> sonic performance from Dawamesk &amp; Maurice Charles JJ<br /> <a href=\"http://www.nohmad.net/html/netlabel.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nohmad.net/<wbr />html/netlabel.html</a><br /> <br /> ê—ˆCuspN (Brussels, Be)<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/cuspn/jaimepas\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/<wbr />cuspn/jaimepas</a><br /> <a href=\"https://github.com/grirgz\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/grirgz</a><br /> <br /> <br /> 5 euros<br /> <br /> The Student , 76 rue des Palais, 76 Paleizenstraat, 1030 Brussels,<br /> Tram 32, 25 ,93 (Liedts, Lefrancq)</span></span><br /> <br /> More infos : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/376074572536799/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/376074572536799/</a></p>', '07_01_2014_bruxelles_TTT_party.jpg', 0),
(19, '2014-01-25', 'CCL \r\n4 Rue de Colmar 59000 Lille', 'Lille - TTT & TTanker', '<p><strong>TTT &amp; TTanker</strong><br /> <br /> <span class=\"fsl\">Lives:<br /> <br /> ê—ˆ C_C (TTT/ Bedroom Research, Paris)<br /> <br /> ê—ˆTerrificolor (TTT, Paris )<br /> <br /> ê—ˆ Meconium (TTanker, Lille)<br /> <br /> ê—ˆ Exoterrism (TTT, Bxl)<br /> <br /> Visuals:<br /> <br /> ê—ˆ CCCPu (TTT, Bxl)<br /> <br /> ê—ˆ Tzky (TTanker, Lille)<br /> <br /> ê—ˆ Marguerite (TTanker, Lille)</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThirdTypeTapes\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ThirdTypeTapes</a></span></p>\r\n<p>More infos : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/807285255963655\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/807285255963655</a></p>', '25_01_2014_lille_TTT_TTanker.jpg', 0),
(20, '2014-02-14', 'La Poissonnerie\r\n214 Rue du Progres \r\n1030 Schaerbeek', 'organik vibes bis live', '<p><strong>OGANIK VIBES: 1BisLIVE Concerts+Projections DIA+SUPER8</strong><span class=\"fsl\"><br /> <br /> La Poissonnerie (Rue du Progr&egrave;s 214).<br /> <br /> <span class=\"text_exposed_show\">(EN) Radio performance, a mix of cheerfulness and positive energy.<br /> <br /> Line up:<br /> <br /> DJ VLADI G-Techno/Latin&amp;Balkans,<br /> EXOTERRISM- Live coding<br /> SAM RUSHTON - psych&eacute; rythms<br /> NEVROZ -solid soundscapes<br /> BOB&eacute; Van J&eacute;zu - abstract mix<br /> <br /> GROOVEBOX VJ,<br /> CCCPU VJ...<br /> <br /> Djembe, sax, violin, synthesizer ... People can bring their instruments for a very l\'organik\' live music playing with DJ VLADI G. Also bring your super8 films or slide... They will be projected during the performance!!!<br /> <br /> Prix Libres , PWYW,<br /> <br /> Doors 19h30 Trams (Thomas):3,25,55,93,9,32<br /> <a href=\"http://studio1bis.be/\" target=\"_blank\">www.studio1bis.be</a></span></span></p>\r\n<p>More infos : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1404262993156868/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1404262993156868/</a></p>', '14_02_2014_bruxelles_organik_vibes.jpg', 0);
