(29, '2014-04-24', 'Le Lautrec \r\n63 rue Jean Baptiste Pigalle \r\n75009 Paris', 'Paris - TTT 2xRelease party', '<p><span class=\"fsl\">Third Type Tapes<br /> Double release party TTT08 / TTT09<br /> <br /> Holzkopf (TTT, Here\'s My Card Records, Toztizok Zoundz) &gt; Jungle Noise XP, nouvelle sortie sur TTT<br /> <br /> <span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/holzkopf666\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/<wbr />holzkopf666</a><br /> <a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/holzkopf666/main\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/<wbr />site/holzkopf666/main</a><br /> dub mixing techniques with extreme noise performance and psychedelic walls of sound with harsh static rhythms. The use of cassette decks features heavily in their work, using home-made collage tapes as well as found ones.<br /> <br /> <br /> Ilill (TTT) &gt; Duo Bruit Pop, nouvelle sortie sur TTT<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/thirdtypetapes/sets/ttt08-split-nalov_nalov\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/<wbr />thirdtypetapes/sets/<wbr />ttt08-split-nalov_nalov</a><br /> <a href=\"http://ilillilillilill.wordpress.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://<wbr />ilillilillilill.wordpress.c<wbr />om/</a><br /> le c&oelig;ur veut sortir de la poitrine<br /> guitares chants et percussions noy&eacute;s loin l&agrave;-bas<br /> s&rsquo;arrachent pour faire chanter les cris<br /> le c&oelig;ur ne l&acirc;che pas<br /> <br /> <br /> Evil Moisture (Pure, School of meat cutting...) &gt; Meat Bending / Flesh Noise<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/evil-moisture\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/<wbr />evil-moisture</a><br /> \"Parmi les humano&iuml;des de l&rsquo;anti-culture contamin&eacute;s gravitant autour de la tour des fauch&eacute;s, appara&icirc;t Andy Bolus, musi-m&eacute;canicien fabriquant des jouets mutants aux sonorit&eacute;s d&eacute;mentes et incontr&ocirc;lables.\" Franq de Quango (BimboTower).<br /> <br /> <br /> Klaten (Darling Dada) &gt; Choupi-Core<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/klatentwiz\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/<wbr />klatentwiz</a><br /> <a href=\"http://www.darlingdada.com/artists/klaten/\" target=\"_blank\">http://<wbr />www.darlingdada.com/<wbr />artists/klaten/</a><br /> Sorte de croisement entre un m&eacute;nestrel, un d&eacute;mon et un hochet, Klaten touche &agrave; tout passant all&eacute;grement d\'un style musical &agrave; l\'autre, parfois au sein d\'un m&ecirc;me morceau. Le r&eacute;sultat est g&eacute;n&eacute;reux, spontan&eacute; et diablement efficace.<br /> <br /> <br /> Cracked movies &gt; Apologie du Rien &amp; Plagiat<br /> <br /> <a href=\"http://www.cracked-movies.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://<wbr />www.cracked-movies.com/</a><br /> <a href=\"http://www.mixcloud.com/crackedmovies/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mixcloud.com/<wbr />crackedmovies/</a><br /> <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/crackvo\" target=\"_blank\">http://vimeo.com/crackvo</a><br /> Cracked Movies fabrique des exp&eacute;riences de saturations de fr&eacute;quences et de glitch vid&eacute;o. Par les techniques de surimpressions et de superpositions, elle favorise une culture de la r&eacute;-appropriation, du remake. Privil&eacute;giant la r&eacute;sistance artistique contre la standardisation croissante, ses films sont l\'exp&eacute;rimentation d\'une gen&egrave;se de la destruction. Le glitch a une valeur symbolique de virus. Depuis peu, Cracked Movies cr&eacute;e Crack\'Vo et d&eacute;cline son esth&eacute;tisme au son.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"fsl\"><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">entr&eacute;e 5 Euros</span></span><br /> More infos : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1485921908292950/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1485921908292950/</a></p>', '24_04_2014_paris_TTT.jpg', 0),
(30, '2014-05-10', 'La Cantine De Belleville\r\n108 boulevard de Belleville \r\n75020 Paris', 'Paris - CMPTR MTHMTS', '<p><span class=\"fsl\"><span class=\"text_exposed_show\">C_C with Arnaud Riviere<br /> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/c_c\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/c_c</a><br /> --------------------------<wbr />--<br /> SAINT TITUS<br /> Usually plays guitar &amp; bass in Projet Piscine.<br /> impro solo set - fight walk in confusion / clear doom<br /> --------------------------<wbr />----<br /> DJOEW<br /> Then he will have to try to operate according to two contradictory maps. This is not a recipe for peace of mind. Question the possibility of failure and the threat of inner collapse but never stop looking for new solutions and try to play songs.<br /> <a href=\"http://embah-djoew.blogspot.fr/\" target=\"_blank\">http://<wbr />embah-djoew.blogspot.fr/</a><br /> --------------------------<wbr />----<br /> TRAVIS KERSCHEN<br /> Using energies, physical, emotional, mental and karmic, good, virtuous along with toxic and vicious as a fuel source; love, peace and other ideal states are converted from concepts into physical sensations, with sound (music or noise) and freedom assisting the process; It is possible to go beyond the age of reason and the age of enlightenment. To go beyond the intellect, beyond the emotions and beyond the carnal. To release the light within. This is more significant in the world of brutes, retards, sewage, liars, darkness, antipathy, aggression, dullness, death and rot than in the fertile living world of flowers, harmony, love, peace, wisdom and compassion.<br /> --------------------------<wbr />---<br /> CITY DRAGON<br /> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mOTK5rZEnGo\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/<wbr />watch?v=mOTK5rZEnGo</a></span></span></p>\r\n<p>More infos : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1406390716305711/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1406390716305711/</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '10_05_2014_paris_CMPTR_MTHMTS.jpg', 0),
